hat searching for god knows what more details format — please select — cd mp price updating cart… updating… pages pages    next last » shopping cart your shopping cart is empty visit the shop categories conferences design  living  design  living  design  living  design  living  doing church in a divided world  design  living  entire conference set  speakers alsdorff debbie becky harling boldt sue bright dee carey donna carthen sherwood cheri calcagno currran daniel deanna allen deyoung jane diehl steve dunn kim frink pam goble roy gonzalez nannette guitierrez janice hagen wendy henderson john james cynthia johnson renee johnson rick johnston rachel julia wessels kelly terrance kennedydean jennifer kidder virelle kitely david kristina vandenheuvel lisa harper luck kelli martinez danny meacham gari melissa doppler miller donald minter kelly morales enrique morgan elisa pace kim pomarolli kerri quintrell joanna ramos lisa rigby jill scandrette mark shaffer georgia spitzer todd staci frenes steer lorri tere corey terkeurst lysa tomkins dayspring vernick leslie weber dr catherine hart williams michelle wilson barb wolfe caren yee russel conferences design  living  design  living  design  living  design  living  doing church in a divided world  design  living  entire conference set  speakers alsdorff debbie becky harling boldt sue bright dee carey donna carthen sherwood cheri calcagno currran daniel deanna allen deyoung jane diehl steve dunn kim frink pam goble roy gonzalez nannette guitierrez janice hagen wendy henderson john james cynthia johnson renee johnson rick johnston rachel julia wessels kelly terrance kennedydean jennifer kidder virelle kitely david kristina vandenheuvel lisa harper luck kelli martinez danny meacham gari melissa doppler miller donald minter kelly morales enrique morgan elisa pace kim pomarolli kerri quintrell joanna ramos lisa rigby jill scandrette mark shaffer georgia spitzer todd staci frenes steer lorri tere corey terkeurst lysa tomkins dayspring vernick leslie weber dr catherine hart williams michelle wilson barb wolfe caren yee russel conferences design  living  design  living  design  living  design  living  doing church in a divided world  design  living  entire conference set  speakers alsdorff debbie becky harling boldt sue bright dee carey donna carthen sherwood cheri calcagno currran daniel deanna allen deyoung jane diehl steve dunn kim frink pam goble roy gonzalez nannette guitierrez janice hagen wendy henderson john james cynthia johnson renee johnson rick johnston rachel julia wessels kelly terrance kennedydean jennifer kidder virelle kitely david kristina vandenheuvel lisa harper luck kelli martinez danny meacham gari melissa doppler miller donald minter kelly morales enrique morgan elisa pace kim pomarolli kerri quintrell joanna ramos lisa rigby jill scandrette mark shaffer georgia spitzer todd staci frenes steer lorri tere corey terkeurst lysa tomkins dayspring vernick leslie weber dr catherine hart williams michelle wilson barb wolfe caren yee russel   one way conferences · wordpress · vanilla cart · made by premium wordpress themes donald miller author  wikipedia donald miller author from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search donald miller born august   occupation author public speaker nationality american genre christian spirituality website scaryclosecom donald don miller born august   is a bestselling american author and public speaker based in nashville tennessee who focuses on christian spirituality as an explanation for beauty meaning and the human struggle contents  biography  published works  external links  references biographyedit at  miller left his home in pearland texas and went to portland oregon where he put down roots as he had planned when he started his road trip a few months before millers first book prayer and the art of volkswagen maintenance harvest house publishers  chronicled the crosscountry road trip he took at age  it was printed with little fanfare but it was republished more successfully in  as through painted deserts during this time miller was the editor of an online christian magazine called roadsearchingcom and the owner of a small portlandbased publishing company called coffee house books which published home schooling textbooks miller became a new york times bestselling author when he published blue like jazz in  in  miller released searching for god knows what which explores how the life of jesus illustrates the human personality in  he added another book to own a dragon which offered millers reflections on growing up without a father this book reflected an interest already present in millers life as he founded the mentoring project a nonprofit that partners with local churches to mentor fatherless young men dons next book a million miles in a thousand years was released in late  later that year miller began production of all things converge a series of dvds for small groups that feature miller interviewing prominent christian writers and theologians the first three dvds in the series were released in the fourth quarter of  miller also served as the founding director of the burnside writers collective a group of spiritual writers who contributed to an online magazine miller is recognized for his view that christian faith should be a relationship rather than a formula he writes in searching for god knows what that too many christians act like the bible is a sort of math textbook rather than a long story of gods involvement with people through friendships with biblical figures like adam abraham and moses this emphasis on the bible as a narrative has made his writings popular with many involved in the emerging church conversation miller does not consider himself a follower of the movement he still recognizes the need of mankind to recognize its depravity so that it might better teach the concept of love on november   donald miller married elizabeth miltenberger they now live in nashville tennessee with their chocolate lab lucy miller is also the founder of storyline and storybrand storyline is a life coaching service that connects with its users through conferences books and a blog storybrand is a marketing service published worksedit prayer and the art of volkswagen maintenance finding god on the open road  harvest house publishers note republished as through painted deserts blue like jazz nonreligious thoughts on christian spirituality  nelson books searching for god knows what  nelson books through painted deserts light god and beauty on the open road  nelson books to own a dragon reflections on growing up without a father  navpress note expanded and republished as father fiction a million miles in a thousand years fall  nelson books father fiction chapters for a fatherless generation storyline finding your subplot in gods story  donald miller words llc scary close  nelson external linksedit wikiquote has quotations related to donald miller author storyline website storybrand website donald miller facebook page donald miller twitter page donald miller instagram page referencesedit  miller donald  blue like jazz denver tennessee nelson books   httpmodernmarchwordpresscomtheemergingchurchmovement v t e donald miller blue like jazz film searching for god knows what a million miles in a thousand years authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     gnd x bnf cb data musicbrainz ebabdaeaeb retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitledonaldmillerauthoroldid categories living peoplepeople from houstonwriters from portland oregon birthsamerican christiansreed college alumniwriters from texasamerican male writerschristian bloggershidden categories use mdy dates from july wikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifierswikipedia articles with isni identifierswikipedia articles with gnd identifierswikipedia articles with bnf identifierswikipedia articles with musicbrainz identifiers navigation menu personal tools not 